---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for PDF Table to Excel."
  canonicalPath="/terms/"
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p>This tool is provided for lightweight PDF table extraction. You are responsible for verifying exported data before using it for business, finance, legal, or compliance decisions.</p>
    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>Do not upload files you are not authorized to process. Do not use automated traffic to bypass rate limits.</p>
    <h2>Accuracy</h2>
    <p>PDF table extraction can be imperfect, especially with complex layouts, merged cells, and multi-page tables. Always review the output.</p>
    <h2>Availability</h2>
    <p>Limits, features, and availability may change as the tool improves.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
